title: Tajikistan Fiscal Expenditure
description: Fiscal Expenditure in Tajikistan increased to 16869.20 TJS Million in July from 14141.20 TJS Million in June of 2022. Fiscal Expenditure in Tajikistan averaged 5046.63 TJS Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 29295 TJS Million in December of 2021 and a record low of 5.30 TJS Million in January of 2000. This page provides - Tajikistan Fiscal Expenditure- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National bank of Tajikistan
